NB. interp01
NB. x is a list of values representing equal-spaced intervals from 0 to 1
NB. y is a list of numbers in range from 0 to 1
NB. result is interpolated values from x corresponding to y
interp01=: 3 : 0
y=. y * <: #x
b=. x {~ <.y
t=. x {~ >.y
k=. y - <.y
(t*k) + b*-.k
)

